{"tid":1318480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家輿論導向：發起聯署「香港要平和」","createTime":"2019-07-15T02:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T03:46:04.000Z","uid":261842,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"769658d2ffabc6876a58358ee67f561239a040b0","tid":1318480,"uid":261842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"又係5年前D野咁啦：<br />\n<br />\n1.）又打民生要平和牌<br />\n2.）叫政府加大力度做野<br />\n3.）叫搵個人做大台（然後一獲煮起佢）<br />\n<br />\n唔好話，佢呢個title真係吸到街坊buy的<br />\n文宣有無辦法拆？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下是TG gp內流傳的內容：<br />\n（Btw佢 TG gp又講鳥合之眾.....）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#靜一靜停一停香港要平和<br />\n#聯署聲明<br />\n<br />\n7.1 示威者攻佔立法會<br />\n7.7 旺角黑夜<br />\n7.13 上水衝突<br />\n7.14 沙田流血<br />\n夠了！真的夠了！<br />\n<br />\n各方要冷靜<br />\n社區要安寧<br />\n香港需要平靜下來<br />\n<br />\n不斷集會只會不斷爆發衝突，<br />\n使青年受傷、警察受損、市民撕裂...<br />\n夠了！真的夠了！<br />\n<br />\n我們要求：<br />\n1. 各方團體勿再搞遊行集會令衝突及對立惡化<br />\n2. 政府及警方勿再發出集會的「不反對通知書」<br />\n3. 示威者推舉及委派代表與政府商討善後<br />\n<br />\n聯署方式：<br />\n1. 直接到網站聯署 <a href=\"http://tiny.cc/t8ap9y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftiny.cc%2Ft8ap9y&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=fbcc3cc9\" target=\"_blank\">tiny.cc/t8ap9y</a><br />\n2. 發送文字：「香港要平和」 到<br />\n    I. 電郵到 <a href=\"http://joint.statement.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjoint.statement.hk&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=bf5c0a65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">joint.statement.hk</a>@gmail.com 或<br />\n    II. SMS 短訊 到 5531 2691 或<br />\n    III. Whatsapp / WeChat  到 5531 2691<br />\n<br />\n發起：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/LionRockHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLionRockHK%2F&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=9ab4e359\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/LionRockHK/</a>"},{"pid":"e30eb412f6013caf04a96d96be1b3e39587ae9ab","tid":1318480,"uid":261842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T03:43:21.000Z","msg":"講真金日好多5毛上哂水係各大FB PAGES維穩，<br /